1
00:00:07,620 --> 00:00:10,360
It feels fulfilling,

2
00:00:10,360 --> 00:00:13,140
but I'm spending my days aimlessly.

3
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:25,610
Like any other high schooler,

4
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:29,580
my mind is filled with temporary worries.

5
00:00:30,350 --> 00:00:36,180
I keep an exaggerated distance between those around me.

6
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:41,490
A bit of boredom is just right.

7
00:00:42,230 --> 00:00:44,910
It's easier to deal with those who are awkward.

8
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:49,190
Afraid of looking stupid when expressing myself,

9
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:52,710
I pretend because of my youth.

10
00:01:00,980 --> 00:01:02,940
That's why I thought...

11
00:01:05,290 --> 00:01:07,890
this must be the same kind of thing.

12
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:11,820
That's what I thought at first.

13
