00:01:48,820 --> 00:01:52,650
♫ Just take in everything, everything, everything ♫

18
00:01:52,650 --> 00:01:56,900
♫ Don't worry about getting burned ♫

19
00:01:56,900 --> 00:02:01,630
♫ The reason why I wish to see a tomorrow that would stop my tears ♫

20
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:06,920
♫ I found the present within you that suppresses  ♫

21
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:13,008
♫ The future we're heading for ♫
